A 44-year-old Kenyan nurse has been charged with raping an elderly woman in the United States.Thomas Kamau Nganga was reported by his colleague who caught him forcing himself on a 72-year-old patient.An administrator at the nursing home where Mr Nganga worked, Lexington Rehabilitation and Healthcare in Richmond, Virginia, said the suspect was fired after he was arrested.Mr Nganga was detained at Henrico County Jail with no bond and is due in court in December.According to court documents, Nganga is married and with children, ABC 8News reported.  